# ── lanthanides.io — example environment ─────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to `.env` for local development. `.env` is gitignored — never commit it,
# and never put real credentials or paid-service keys here (CLAUDE.md hard rule).
#
# Local/dev database: a SQLite file in the project root. Production switches the
# Prisma datasource provider to `postgresql` by changing ONLY this connection
# string — no code change (docs/MIGRATION.md §1).
DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"
